OL,3,CWelsh politicians in the Senedd set
OL,4,Cfor 6% pay rise
OL,6,FMembers of the Senedd could receive a
OL,7,F6% pay rise this year.
OL,9,FThe rise would mean a backbench Senedd
OL,10,Fmember would earn #76,380 a year from
OL,11,FApril, up from #72,057 in 2024.
OL,13,FProposals for a 6% increase in MSs'
OL,14,Fpay have been put forward by the
OL,15,FIndependent Remuneration Board (the
OL,16,Fbody responsible for ensuring Members
OL,17,Fof the Senedd have the appropriate
OL,18,Fmoney and resources available to
OL,19,Fthem), as part of its annual review
OL,20,Fpublished on Wednesday.
