OL,3,CWelsh politicians in the Senedd set
OL,4,Cfor 6% pay rise
OL,6,FThe First Minister, Eluned Morgan,
OL,7,Fwould see her additional salary rise
OL,8,Fto #90,701, taking her total pay to
OL,9,F#167,081, while senior government
OL,10,Fministers would get #119,343.
OL,12,FThe pay rise would also mean the
OL,13,FLlywydd ` the presiding officer `
OL,14,Fwould see her salary increase to
OL,15,F#125,310.
OL,17,FThe increase is now subject to a
OL,18,Fpublic consultation.
