OL,3,CWelsh politicians in the Senedd set
OL,4,Cfor 6% pay rise
OL,6,FDr Elizabeth Haywood, chairwoman of
OL,7,Fthe remuneration board said the
OL,8,Fincrease took into account "changing
OL,9,Fcircumstances and inflationary
OL,10,Fpressure".
OL,12,FShe said: "The latest average earnings
OL,13,Ffigure for 2023/24, published in
OL,14,FNovember, has confirmed a three-year
OL,15,Fperiod of unexpected and consistent
OL,16,Fgrowth in average salaries.
