OL,3,CWelsh politicians in the Senedd set
OL,4,Cfor 6% pay rise
OL,6,F"Retaining the 3% cap on members' pay,
OL,7,Fwhich has been in place since 2021,
OL,8,Fwould contradict this principle and
OL,9,Fthe board therefore proposes an
OL,10,Fincrease of 6% in line with the latest
OL,11,FAnnual Survey of Hours and Earnings
OL,12,Ffigures for Wales."
