OL,3,CWelsh politicians in the Senedd set
OL,4,Cfor 6% pay rise
OL,6,FShe added: "The board's review focused
OL,7,Fon its core objectives and principles
OL,8,Fto ensure members are remunerated
OL,9,Ffairly and provided with sufficient
OL,10,Fresources to support them in their
OL,11,Fduties, whilst ensuring that decisions
OL,12,Fare appropriate within the wider
OL,13,Ffinancial circumstances of Wales and
OL,14,Frepresent value for money."
OL,16,FThe increase is in line with pay
OL,17,Fincreases at other UK parliaments in
OL,18,Frecent years, with MPs and Scotland's
OL,19,FMSPs receiving 5.5% and 6.7% pay rises
OL,20,Frespectively last year.
